folder: Kane Street & Tompkins Place, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Kane Street, at the S.E. corner of Tompkins Place, showing the Beth Israel Synagogue. View 2 is east on Kane Street to Court Street. The low building to the left of the synagogue is the Sabbath school.

P. L. Sperr

View 1: June 6, 1933
View 2: October 15, 1940
